    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the <strong>pulled mushrooms</strong> to the pan with your <strong>hoisin sauce</strong>,<strong> soy sauce</strong> and a splash of <strong>cold water</strong> and cook for 2 min or until warmed through – these are your <strong>shredded hoisin mushrooms</strong></p>",
